1. Ne želim da radim sa *lošim* kolegom. (I don't want to work with a *bad* colleague.)
2. Moramo se osloboditi *loših* navika. (We need to get rid of *bad* habits.)
3. *Lošem* vremenu se ne radujemo. (We don't look forward to *bad* weather.)
4. Njegov uspeh je posledica *lošeg* upravljanja. (His success is a result of *poor* management.)
5. *Loše* mi je od te hrane. (I feel *sick* from that food.)
6. Nemoj da me nerviraš, već sam u *lošem* raspoloženju. (Don't annoy me, I'm already in a *bad* mood.)
7. On je bio iznenađen *lošom* vesti. (He was surprised by the *bad* news.)
8. Čini mi se da imamo *lošu* vezu. (It seems to me that we have a *poor* connection.)
9. Uspeli smo da popravimo *loše* odnose sa komšijom. (We managed to improve *bad* relations with our neighbor.)
10. Nije bilo *loše* predstave, ali nisam oduševljen. (The play wasn't *bad*, but I'm not thrilled.)